<GuideLayout
  title="UK Tax Year 2026/27 – Complete Guide to Rates & Thresholds"
  description="Everything you need to know about UK tax rates for the 2026/27 tax year. Income tax bands, National Insurance, student loan thresholds, and pension rules."
